            "SCN_002_SHOT_006"
          ],
          "beat_type": "action",
          "scene_tone": null,
          "emotional_beat_index": 0.27
        },
        {
          "scene_id": "SCN_003",
          "characters": [
            "WORKER",
            "NARA"
          ],
          "character_ids": [
            "worker",
            "nara"
          ],
          "location": "INT. PRESSURE VALVE CHAMBER - NIGHT",
          "location_id": "int_pressure_valve_chamber_night",
          "time_of_day": "night",
          "visual_actions": [
            "Nara stabilizes a failing valve while exhausted workers keep their distance.",
            "The alarm dies and the chamber returns to white light.",
            "Nara looks at the hidden route on her wrist and understands that something is wrong."
          ],
          "dialogues": [
            "You just saved half the block.",
            "Who signed the last maintenance map update?",
            "Central Authority. Same as always."
          ],
          "emotion": "neutral",
          "action_units": [],
          "shot_ids": [
            "SCN_003_SHOT_001",
            "SCN_003_SHOT_002",
            "SCN_003_SHOT_003",
            "SCN_003_SHOT_004",
            "SCN_003_SHOT_005"
          ],
          "beat_type": "action",
          "scene_tone": null,
          "emotional_beat_index": 0.34
        },
        {
          "scene_id": "SCN_004",
          "characters": [
            "NARA",
            "ELIAN"
          ],
          "character_ids": [
            "nara",
            "elian"
          ],
          "location": "INT. VOSS APARTMENT - LOWER STACK - LATE NIGHT",
          "location_id": "int_voss_apartment_lower_stack_late_night",
          "time_of_day": "night",
          "visual_actions": [
            "In their cramped apartment, Nara shows the captured route to her father, Elian.",
            "He freezes when he sees the unlisted access spine."
          ],
          "dialogues": [
            "This showed up inside a live stack map and then vanished.",
            "Forget it.",
            "Then why are you scared of a corridor?",
            "Because in this city, hidden doors are never just doors."
          ],
          "emotion": "neutral",
          "action_units": [],
          "shot_ids": [
            "SCN_004_SHOT_001",
            "SCN_004_SHOT_002",
            "SCN_004_SHOT_003",
            "SCN_004_SHOT_004"
          ],
          "beat_type": "climax",
          "scene_tone": null,
          "emotional_beat_index": 0.41
        },
        {
          "scene_id": "SCN_005",
          "characters": [
            "VALE",
            "AIDE"
          ],
          "character_ids": [
            "vale",
            "aide"
          ],
          "location": "INT. CIVIC ATRIUM - DISTRICT ZERO CENTRAL CORE - MORNING",
          "location_id": "int_civic_atrium_district_zero_central_core_morning",
          "time_of_day": "interior",
          "visual_actions": [
            "Director Halden Rook addresses the district from giant public screens while citizens move through an immaculate civic atrium.",
            "Above them, Commander Sarin Vale watches from a glass balcony as an aide hands him a security alert tied to Nara."
          ],
          "dialogues": [
            "Put her under passive watch.",
            "Detain?",
            "No. If she found one door, I want to know whether she can find the next."
          ],
          "emotion": "neutral",
          "action_units": [],
          "shot_ids": [
            "SCN_005_SHOT_001",
            "SCN_005_SHOT_002",
            "SCN_005_SHOT_003",
            "SCN_005_SHOT_004"
          ],
          "beat_type": "climax",
          "scene_tone": null,
          "emotional_beat_index": 0.48
        },
        {
          "scene_id": "SCN_006",
          "characters": [
            "LOW LIGHT",
            "MIRA",
            "NARA"
          ],
          "character_ids": [
            "low_light",
            "mira",
            "nara"
          ],
          "location": "INT. BLACK MARKET EXCHANGE - VENTILATION SUBLEVEL - DAY",
          "location_id": "int_black_market_exchange_ventilation_sublevel_day",
          "time_of_day": "day",
          "visual_actions": [
            "Mira Sol studies Nara's stolen map and overlays it with archived infrastructure.",
            "Mira reaches into her bag and opens an archived signal map on the table.",
            "A new route suddenly erupts on the display, leading toward the outer wall."
          ],
          "dialogues": [
            "An illegal signal market hums beneath the transit network.",
            "This isn't erased infrastructure. It's masked infrastructure.",
            "Can you open it?",
            "Probably. The better question is whether you survive after I do."
          ],
          "emotion": "neutral",
          "action_units": [],
          "shot_ids": [
            "SCN_006_SHOT_001",
            "SCN_006_SHOT_002",
            "SCN_006_SHOT_003",
            "SCN_006_SHOT_004",
            "SCN_006_SHOT_005"
          ],
          "beat_type": "climax",
          "scene_tone": null,
          "emotional_beat_index": 0.55
        },
        {
          "scene_id": "SCN_007",
          "characters": [
            "VALE"
          ],
          "character_ids": [
            "vale"
          ],
          "location": "INT. SECURITY OPERATIONS CENTER - DAY",
          "location_id": "int_security_operations_center_day",
          "time_of_day": "day",
          "visual_actions": [
            "Analysts track Nara's movement across a live schematic of the city.",
            "Vale watches her path converge on the outer sectors and chooses not to stop her."
          ],
          "dialogues": [
            "If she reaches the gate, I want to know what she thinks she saw."
          ],
          "emotion": "neutral",
          "action_units": [],
          "shot_ids": [
            "SCN_007_SHOT_001",
            "SCN_007_SHOT_002",
            "SCN_007_SHOT_003",
            "SCN_007_SHOT_004"
          ],
          "beat_type": "dialogue_scene",
          "scene_tone": null,
          "emotional_beat_index": 0.62
        },
        {
          "scene_id": "SCN_008",
          "characters": [
            "NARA"
          ],
          "character_ids": [
            "nara"
          ],
          "location": "INT. SEALED SERVICE SPINE - NIGHT",
          "location_id": "int_sealed_service_spine_night",
          "time_of_day": "night",
          "visual_actions": [
            "Nara and Mira descend into an old service corridor buried in the skeleton of the city.",
            "Mira powers up a buried control panel while Nara watches the dark passage behind them.",
            "The system identifies an external containment access route.",
            "Mira unlocks the gate."
          ],
          "dialogues": [
            "Containment from what?"
          ],
          "emotion": "neutral",
          "action_units": [],
          "shot_ids": [
            "SCN_008_SHOT_001",
            "SCN_008_SHOT_002",
            "SCN_008_SHOT_003",
